{"id": 57812, "date": "2025-07-24T04:00:04", "date_gmt": "2025-07-24T11:00:04", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57812"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T11:12:19", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T18:12:19", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-24-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/24/kingdom-of-days-july-24-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 24"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1968:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles play a gig at Le Teendezvous in New Shrewsbury, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3162\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1968-0724/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0724.jpg?fit=389%2C557&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"389,557\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1968-0724\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0724.jpg?fit=210%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0724.jpg?fit=389%2C557&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3162 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0724.jpg?resize=389%2C557&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"389\" height=\"557\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0724.jpg?w=389&amp;ssl=1 389w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1968-0724.jpg?resize=210%2C300&amp;ssl=1 210w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 389px) 100vw, 389px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1973: </strong>Bruce works on mixing and overdubs for &#8220;Seaside Bar Song&#8221; and &#8220;Kitty&#8217;s Back&#8221; at 914 Sound Studios in Blauvelt, New York.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>The Born to Run Tour is already underway, but the album\u00a0<em>still</em> isn&#8217;t finished. Bruce hustles back from his sow in Stockbridge the night before to record a new verse and bridge for &#8220;She&#8217;s the One&#8221; at the Record Plant in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce takes ill and must postpone his scheduled Rosemont show to September.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28436\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-07-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-23.jpg?fit=1347%2C856&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1347,856\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-07-23\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-23.jpg?fit=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-23.jpg?fit=758%2C482&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28436 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-23.jpg?resize=758%2C482&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"482\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-23.jpg?w=1347&amp;ssl=1 1347w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-23.jpg?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-23.jpg?resize=1024%2C651&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1981-07-23.jpg?resize=768%2C488&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>At Night Two in Toronto on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour, Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Trapped.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-ul3sptBK-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/ul3sptBK?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1999:</strong> Night Four of fifteen at the Meadowlands at the opening stand of the U.S. Reunion Tour features the tour premiere of &#8220;Point Blank,&#8221; its first performance in 14 years, recast in a new contemplative arrangement.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HPdJWh3R5x8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce takes Matt Lauer on a tour of Asbury Park for an upcoming segment of\u00a0<em>The Today Show</em>. They end their tour at Sonny&#8217;s Southern Cuisine, where Bruce plays &#8220;I&#8217;ve Got a Feeling (Everything&#8217;s Gonna Be Alright&#8221; and &#8220;My City of Ruins&#8221; on his acoustic guitar. The segment will air on July 29th.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/W5A6P8r3emk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19788\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-07-24/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?fit=1662%2C1334&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1662,1334\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2002-07-24\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?fit=300%2C241&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?fit=758%2C608&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19788 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?resize=758%2C608&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?w=1662&amp;ssl=1 1662w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?resize=300%2C241&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?resize=1024%2C822&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?resize=768%2C616&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-24.png?resize=1536%2C1233&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>Night Four of the ten-night Giants Stadium stand on the Rising Tour features a rare &#8220;Streets of Fire&#8221; in the opening pack.</p>\n<div id=\"v-2Mij3jw4-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/2Mij3jw4?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-oHoE4Uus-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/oHoE4Uus?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays a solo acoustic show at the Charlotte Coliseum, one of only two shows on the entire summer leg without at least one tour premiere.</p>\n<div id=\"v-1YABZAFn-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/1YABZAFn?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19790\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2005-07-24/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2005-07-24.png?fit=655%2C1752&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"655,1752\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2005-07-24\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2005-07-24.png?fit=112%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2005-07-24.png?fit=383%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19790 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2005-07-24.png?resize=655%2C1752&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"655\" height=\"1752\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2005-07-24.png?w=655&amp;ssl=1 655w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2005-07-24.png?resize=112%2C300&amp;ssl=1 112w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2005-07-24.png?resize=383%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 383w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2005-07-24.png?resize=574%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 574w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 655px) 100vw, 655px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce opens Night Two in Bergen with an acoustic &#8220;Long Walk Home&#8221; (a Wrecking Ball tour premiere). The show features four additional tour premieres, including the live debut of &#8220;You&#8217;ve Got It,&#8221; the first full-band &#8220;This Depression,&#8221; and rare outings for &#8220;My Lucky Day&#8221; and &#8220;Red Headed Woman.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/U1TUxEH0Gyw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5SvhxN-ifKY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/90JKjWbuNDY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RD90JKjWbuNDY\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2013: </strong>As the Wrecking Ball Tour nears its end, the tour premieres continue to delight and astound. At this show in Leeds, Bruce pulls out back-to-back-to-back premieres of &#8220;Local Hero,&#8221; &#8220;Gotta Get That Feeling&#8221; and &#8220;Bad Moon Rising,&#8221; and an ultra-rare &#8220;Secret Garden&#8221; opens the encores, accompanied by Bruce&#8217;s heartfelt dedication to travelling fans. This show is available for purchase as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ELEGhf7dMJw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9TTcrhfRjjM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dMriDhHDB1E?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3rWAygcoOsI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JxN53Liuxe4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cZbPnO2jyBY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City. Beck is in attendance tonight.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"11485\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/beck/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/beck.jpg?fit=500%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"500,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"beck\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/beck.jpg?fit=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/beck.jpg?fit=500%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-11485 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/beck.jpg?resize=500%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/beck.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/beck.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/beck.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/beck.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>On this date: the live debut of &#8220;You Got It,&#8221; the long awaited return of &#8220;Point Blank,&#8221; a Boss-guided tour of Asbury Park, and a stunner of a show in Leeds.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 11486, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [2], "tags": [62, 1099, 558, 424, 61, 783, 610, 1278, 1243, 1331, 1329, 860, 537, 736, 367, 376, 293, 578, 1330, 28, 706, 445], "class_list": ["post-57812", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-kingdom-of-days", "tag-asbury-pa